{"tid":1835780,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"你地屋企隻貓會唔會好似我呢隻咁","createTime":"2020-01-23T03:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T08:25:25.000Z","uid":114062,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"344814af484136f4a8074781cd4dd8a851a2d38d","tid":1835780,"uid":114062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T03:19:53.000Z","msg":"代po<br />\n好撚識刷鞋<br />\n我老母一番到去又攬住佢隻腳<br />\n又自己行去佢隔離喵佢<br />\n主動用個頭去貼我老母塊面到<br />\n相反 <br />\n我一番到 最多都即刻出來望下我<br />\n我會好主動咁抱佢 <br />\n抱唔夠1分鐘又自己走左去<br />\n同佢鼻對鼻 比佢四肢撐撚行曬 <br />\n唔比我痴埋佢到 <br />\n訓教自己上床訓床尾 <br />\n攬佢去我隔離訓又自己行番去床尾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不推文回覆唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5d8aecb217bc107614d5f6d216410eca374bf8","tid":1835780,"uid":8439,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T03:20:59.000Z","msg":"剷屎官都有分高低級OK?"},{"pid":"28e5664d7c6d77e97076036c76f715f15c0ea305","tid":1835780,"uid":114062,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"de5d8aecb217bc107614d5f6d216410eca374bf8","tid":1835780,"uid":8439,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T03:20:59.000Z","msg":"剷屎官都有分高低級OK?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T03:22:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10326fe9ce6c635d2cbca6af5a0e38953f364779","tid":1835780,"uid":303794,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T03:25:03.000Z","msg":"好打耳！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我個啲仲細 所以應該未識住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377dc49a16747202da9befc4cc50d4fe5bd75427","tid":1835780,"uid":114062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10326fe9ce6c635d2cbca6af5a0e38953f364779","tid":1835780,"uid":30